{"tid":1763324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足整緊 失蹤者資料庫？","createTime":"2019-11-30T08:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T11:13:15.000Z","uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"275170d10f1a2c88b0f25e44ba108e1d87a9ba63","tid":1763324,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ee875789054c4067130e1696644c071d12630a","tid":1763324,"uid":274161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>文字記者 梁嘉麗</strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/realityisbrutal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frealityisbrutal%2F&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b3c6d3f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/realityisbrutal/</a><br />\n【他們不能被消失】<br />\n用工餘時間做資料搜集和整理，做得很慢，這兩天只做了五十幾個，要逐個post看亦要細閱留言看是否已聯絡上。個人的力量很微不足道，但有些事情還是必須做。太多消失了的手足，實在不能坐視不理，很多人都說做database是非常迫切，卻看不見有人正在實行。<br />\n格式大概如此，現從某些群組搜集大約五十多個失蹤手足，還在更新中，將會於日內把資料公布，協助尋人，感謝各位。<br />\n若有近期失蹤手足的資訊，歡迎PM。<br />\n＃尋人 ＃失蹤人口 ＃被消失的手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fsin9-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/78674955_156837335693255_4564140464172695552_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=GXzU9dQ6Gf0AQmS-JjLYFJw3g2NvlZ4zRxLdNS0-QbTw24g3vVZDqNyKQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fsin9-1.fna&amp;oh=f4a0daeff0153a890630fbcddcdcfd62&amp;oe=5E84C499\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fsin9-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F78674955_156837335693255_4564140464172695552_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DGXzU9dQ6Gf0AQmS-JjLYFJw3g2NvlZ4zRxLdNS0-QbTw24g3vVZDqNyKQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fsin9-1.fna%26oh%3Df4a0daeff0153a890630fbcddcdcfd62%26oe%3D5E84C499&h=0e3d2ad3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a18df91f6a0441ad6644344338183abdf556e6f","tid":1763324,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ee875789054c4067130e1696644c071d12630a","tid":1763324,"u